mean_cn: phr. 跳爆竹（一种跳跃运动，跳起时双腿展开，双手在头顶接触，然后恢复到双脚并拢，手臂垂放在身体两侧的姿势）
mean_en: a form of exercise in which one jumps from a standing position, with the feet together and the arms at the sides, to a position in which the feet are apart and the hands touch overhead, and then jumps back again
sentence: Jumping jacks are an exercise which we often do as a warm-up.
sentence_trans: 跳爆竹是一种我们经常作为热身项目的练习。
